00:03:57.440 --> 00:03:58.360
I can't bear to leave.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:00.600
I'm okay with it.

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.200
I've graduated once before.

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:03.960
You mean middle school?

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:06.480
Yeah.

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:09.000
By the way,

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:10.800
you brought your guitar last night—

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:12.240
was it to play for me?

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.600
So when will you play again?

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:16.520
I want to hear it.

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:22.160
Back to where it all began.

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:25.320
In my memories,

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:28.480
