00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.480
Your profile under the starry sky.

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:37.880
I got the wrong key.

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:39.720
Sing! I'm recording.

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:41.280
