00:04:41.960 --> 00:04:43.000
Off-key is even better.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:43.680
Do another one.

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:44.840
Come on, one more!

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:51.040
Back to where it all began.

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:56.040
Yu Xingchen, not bad!

00:04:56.280 --> 00:04:57.600
So you asked me to teach you guitar

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:58.960
just to play for Su Ruo.

00:04:59.880 --> 00:05:01.480
Ren Nan, what are you doing?

