You're way out of line.

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:22.720
Are you crazy?

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:24.080
Why did you splash water on him?

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.000
Because of the medium interference principle.

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:28.160
Did it cause a tunneling effect interruption?

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:29.680
Wasn't he dizzy?

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:30.960
I wanted to wake him up.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.840
Ren Nan, what are you doing?

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:34.000
Yu Xingchen.

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:35.040
I'm telling you,

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:37.160
watch your behavior from now on.

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:39.520
Don't be a toad lusting after a swan.

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:41.360
This is a warning.

00:05:41.960 --> 00:05:43.560
Warning you not to have foolish hopes.

00:05:47.320 --> 00:05:48.200
Are you alright?

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:52.960
It's raining, remember to dry your hair when you get home.

00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:54.000
Don't catch a cold.

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:57.400
Good thing we have two umbrellas this time.

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:06.600
Su Ruo.

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:10.000
Have you been happy these days?

00:06:11.680 --> 00:06:12.320
Yes, I have.

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:15.720
Then you

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:18.960
should always remember these happy moments.

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:24.240
If I'm ever unhappy one day,

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:25.280
I'll come find you.

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:33.880
My ride's here.

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:35.040
I'm heading off.

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:36.280
See you tomorrow.

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:23.480
See you tomorrow.

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:58.720
Even though I haven't changed anything,

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:02.040
at least I made many beautiful memories for her.

00:09:03.160 --> 00:09:04.520
That's a good thing, I guess.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.920
Stop sleeping.

00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:15.080
Why are you here again?

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:18.360
A friend named Zhang Xun asked you to play ball.

00:09:22.040 --> 00:09:23.880
With his leg, he can still play?

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.760
He probably just wants a free meal.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.640
Let's go, Ning Jing. I'll treat you to lunch.

00:09:31.520 --> 00:09:32.920
Pass the ball! Over here, over here!

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.760
Serve again.

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:39.240
Bro.

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:41.560
Where's your friend?

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.600
I'm wondering too.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.560
I didn't see any wheelchair or crutches.

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.120
Did we get the wrong place?

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:06.920
Girlfriend, huh?

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:11.200
My little sister.

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:13.080
I'd love to be your brother-in-law.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:13.920
Is that okay?

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:17.840
Just kidding, sis. Don't take it seriously.

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:20.320
But think about it for real.

00:10:21.520 --> 00:10:22.640
Stop joking around.

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:25.720
You don't need a cane anymore.

00:10:25.800 --> 00:10:27.320
With my Super Saiyan leg,

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.480
why would I need a cane?

00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:30.880
Did you forget what happened senior year?

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:33.440
Maybe you should change your shoes.

00:10:33.520 --> 00:10:35.040
Those spikes are intense.

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.440
You might hurt someone if you kick them.

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:37.960
Zhang Xun.

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:38.520
Get him to the infirmary, quick!

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:39.760
He has an Achilles tendon rupture.

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:40.480
Don't take him to the infirmary.

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:42.080
Go to the hospital for surgery, now!

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:42.560
Or he'll be crippled.

00:10:42.680 --> 00:10:43.680
I'll go with him to the hospital.

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:44.600
You go back to class.

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:45.720
Please remind the doctor,

00:10:45.720 --> 00:10:46.560
don't delay the surgery.

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:47.600
He needs an Achilles tendon operation ASAP.

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:48.800
Okay, don't worry.

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:51.240
Let me tell you,

00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:51.760
if it weren't for me,

00:10:51.760 --> 00:10:53.440
you'd need a cane for the rest of your life.

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.160
You know that, right?

00:10:54.280 --> 00:10:55.360
You really owe me a thank you.

00:10:56.320 --> 00:10:57.840
You still remember stuff from ages ago.

00:10:58.160 --> 00:10:59.320
Just say you want a free meal.

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.600
After I retired from the provincial team,

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:06.480
the bureau gave us athletes some support.

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:07.800
So I started an online shop.

00:11:08.760 --> 00:11:09.360
Zhang Xun.

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:11.400
Why did you suddenly want to play ball today?

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.400
I ran into someone recently.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.800
It made me think of our high school days.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.200
And I started missing you.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.120
Who did you meet that made you think of high school?

00:11:19.280 --> 00:11:20.000
My first love.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:22.640
Wasn't our first love the same person?

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:25.760
Come on, stop messing around.

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.000
Who did you actually meet?

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:27.960
Ren Nan.

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.040
He's a big boss at a listed company now.

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:32.280
We haven't talked in years.

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:33.560
What?

00:11:33.880 --> 00:11:36.400
You still mind when I mention Ren Nan?

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:37.960
Why would I mind?

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.680
Mind him splashing water in my face?

00:11:40.320 --> 00:11:41.680
It's always a femme fatale.

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:43.240
Getting jealous over Su Ruo.

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:44.480
Su Ruo.

00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:48.640
So her name was Su Ruo.

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.760
I need to tell my sister about this.

00:11:51.880 --> 00:11:52.440
Su Ruo...

00:11:52.760 --> 00:11:55.040
She could've totally been your sister-in-law.

