00:12:02.640 --> 00:12:05.920
I've dedicated songs for many teachers and classmates.

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:08.560
But today's first song

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:11.640
is for my own eighteenth birthday.

00:12:12.280 --> 00:12:14.000
I also want to dedicate it to

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:15.960
all senior year teachers and students.

