00:12:19.760 --> 00:12:20.280
And also,

00:12:20.880 --> 00:12:22.760
I want to say to Zhang Xun from Class Three,

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:24.440
get well soon.

00:12:24.760 --> 00:12:27.240
Everyone in Class Three is waiting for you.

00:12:27.640 --> 00:12:29.080
Su Ruo's last broadcast.

00:12:29.800 --> 00:12:31.480
Weren't you having surgery at that time?

00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:32.960
I didn't record it.

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.680
Ren Nan played it for me a few days ago.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:37.240
I asked him for a copy.

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.680
Thinking back, those days were really nice.

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:43.840
A recording from fifteen years ago.

00:12:43.840 --> 00:12:45.520
Ren Nan kept it all this time.

00:12:45.880 --> 00:12:47.440
Does he still like Su Ruo?

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:49.880
You two are both pretty devoted.

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:54.960
Isn't my brother still single too?

00:12:54.960 --> 00:12:57.000
If Su Ruo were still single,

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:58.000
wouldn't there still be a chance?

