00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:23.680
So I went right up to him.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:24.920
Gave him a slap like this—

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:26.560
right on his head.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:27.480
He looked at me and said,

00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:28.440
he said,

00:13:29.560 --> 00:13:31.760
"Zhang Xun, long time no see."

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:33.480
After that,

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:34.600
we had a meal together.

00:13:35.160 --> 00:13:37.160
We both got pretty drunk.

00:13:37.400 --> 00:13:38.520
He passed out.

00:13:39.080 --> 00:13:40.880
His driver and I carried him to the car.

00:13:41.360 --> 00:13:42.440
After we got in, the driver asked,

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:43.680
Boss,

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:44.880
where are we going?

00:13:45.680 --> 00:13:46.440
Ren Nan said,

00:13:47.720 --> 00:13:48.480
"Home."

00:13:50.040 --> 00:13:51.120
The driver asked again,

00:13:51.560 --> 00:13:53.840
Boss, which home do you mean?

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:57.480
Listen to that.

00:13:57.560 --> 00:14:00.240
Sis, which home do you think?

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:01.560
What does that mean?

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:04.120
Isn't it obvious?

00:14:04.400 --> 00:14:07.960
He sure has plenty of places to stay.

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:09.400
Exactly.

00:14:10.040 --> 00:14:11.200
The driver asked several times.

00:14:11.560 --> 00:14:12.520
Ren Nan didn't answer.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:13.960
So I looked over,

00:14:14.280 --> 00:14:15.520
he was already asleep.

00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:16.880
The driver started to panic.

00:14:17.240 --> 00:14:17.960
He looked at the two of us,

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.240
thought we were close buddies.

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:20.880
Scratching his head, he asked me where to go.

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:24.160
I thought, how would I know?

00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:25.440
But I didn't think too much about it.

00:14:25.640 --> 00:14:26.840
Just figured he had lots of homes.

00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:30.000
So I said, just go to whichever is closest.

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:31.920
So the driver got the order,

00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:33.720
and drove straight to Jianshe Community.

